Document: TextServerAdvanced
Path: godot/classes/class_textserveradvanced.rst
Summary: A default Godot TextServer implementation using HarfBuzz, ICU, and SIL Graphite for advanced text layout and OpenType features.

An implementation of TextServer that uses HarfBuzz, ICU and SIL Graphite to support BiDi, complex text layouts and contextual OpenType features. This is Godot's default primary TextServer interface.